readable.content: A brown and black dog on a leash is sniffed by a black and white dog . A dog on a leash walks on the sidewalk while another dog follows . A small dog on a leash is being smelled by another animal . The black and white dog is sniffing the butt of the brown dog that is on a leash . Two small dogs , one black-and-white and one brown-and-black , walk down the street .
